#~ msgid "2012-12-05"
#~ msgstr "2012-12-05"

#~ msgid "2.0.2 (&kde; SC 4.10)"
#~ msgstr "2.0.2 (&kde; SC 4.10)"

#~ msgid "Welcome to <application>Kamoso</application>!"
#~ msgstr "Tete tulemast kasutama <application>Kamosot</application>!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "On launching <application>Kamoso</application>, you are greeted with two "
#~ "groups of buttons on the left and right, and a button in the center."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> käivitamisel ootab sind ees kaks "
#~ "nupurühma vasakul ja paremal ning üks nupp keskel."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The central button helps you to click a picture! Go ahead and try it now! "
#~ "SMILE!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Keskmine nupp aitab teha pilti! Proovi kohe järele! Ja muidugi NAERATA!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> will give you a 3 second heads up so "
#~ "you can pose for your picture, and ask you to smile right before clicking!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> annab 3 sekundit aega ette valmistuda "
#~ "pildi tegemiseks ning palubki sul enne klõpsamist naeratada!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you click on the second button from the left, <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> changes to burst-mode. <application>Kamoso</application> "
#~ "will keep clicking pictures rapidly till you don't click on the center "
#~ "button and tell it to stop. The pictures line up in chronological order "
#~ "on the bottom, and you can view them by double-clicking them. "
#~ "Alternatively, you could right click and choose <guilabel>Open</guilabel> "
#~ "to view the pictures too! If you aren't happy with any of the pictures, "
#~ "just right click and select <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> to delete that "
#~ "particular picture."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui klõpsad vasakult teisele nupule, läheb <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> sarivõtterežiimi. <application>Kamoso</application> hakkab "
#~ "kiiresti üksteise järel pilte tegema, kuni klõpsad taas keskmisele "
#~ "nupule, millega piltide tegemine katkestatakse. Pildid reastatakse "
#~ "kronoloogiliselt akna alaossa ning neid saab vaadata, kui teha pildil "
#~ "topeltklõps. Teine võimalus piltide nägemiseks on teha neil paremklõps ja "
#~ "valida <guilabel>Ava</guilabel>. Kui mõni pilt sulle aga ei meeldi, võid "
#~ "selle kustutada, kui teed paremklõpsu ja valid <guilabel>Viska "
#~ "prügikasti</guilabel>."

#~ msgid "Upload image to Facebook"
#~ msgstr "Pildi laadimine Facebooki"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you feel your newly-clicked pictures must be uploaded to your Facebook "
#~ "profile, just right click on the picture and select <guilabel>Facebook "
#~ "Import/Export</guilabel>. A window will open up on your browser asking "
#~ "you to grant permission to <application>Kamoso</application>. Once you do "
#~ "this, upload away!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui leiad, et vastselt tehtud pildid tuleks kindlasti Facebooki üles "
#~ "laadida, tee pildil paremklõps ja vali <guilabel>Facebooki import/"
#~ "eksport</guilabel>. Sinu veebilehitsejas avatakse seepeale lehekülg, mis "
#~ "palub anda <application>Kamoso</application>le vastava õiguse. Kui see on "
#~ "tehtud, saadki pildi üles laadida."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You need to have an account on Facebook to upload the picture you made"
#~ msgstr "Pildi üleslaadimiseks peab sul loomulikult olema Facebookis konto."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you want to avoid all the right clicks, click on the second button on "
#~ "the right side and you'll be provided with the same options as when you "
#~ "right click."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui sulle miskipärast ei meeldi klõpsata hiire parema nupuga, klõpsa "
#~ "teisele nupule paremalt, mille alt avanevad samasugused valikud nagu "
#~ "paremklõpsul."

#~ msgid "Upload video to YouTube"
#~ msgstr "Video laadimine YouTube'i"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> also allows you to capture videos! By "
#~ "clicking on the red button on the left, you change to video mode. Click "
#~ "on the central button to shoot your video! Right click on the video and "
#~ "select <guilabel>YouTube</guilabel> to upload it to YouTube."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<application>Kamoso</application> võimaldab ka video salvestada! Klõpsuga "
#~ "punasele nupule vasakul saab muuta videorežiimi. Klõpsuga keskmisele "
#~ "nupule saabki video salvestada. Tee videol paremklõps ja vali "
#~ "<guilabel>Youtube</guilabel>, et laadida see kohe Youtube'i."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "You need to have an account on YouTube and provide <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> an access with your username and password – don't worry, "
#~ "it's totally safe!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Sul peab loomulikult olema Youtube'is konto ning <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application>le tuleb kasutajanime ja parooli andes tagada ligipääs - kuid "
#~ "ei tasi karta, see on igati turvaline!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you feel your picture quality isn't optimal, click on the button on "
#~ "the extreme right and select <guilabel>Settings</guilabel>. This is the "
#~ "settings panel."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui arvad, et pildi kvaliteet pole just parim, klõpsa kõige "
#~ "parempoolsemale nupule ja vali <guilabel>Seadistused</guilabel>. See avab "
#~ "seadistustedialoogi."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you want to change the time before <application>Kamoso</application> "
#~ "clicks your picture, navigate to <guilabel>Photo settings</guilabel>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui soovid muuta ooteaega enne seda, kui <application>Kamoso</"
#~ "application> hakkab pilti tegema, vali kaart <guilabel>Fotoseadistused</"
#~ "guilabel>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you're a really technical user, scroll over to the <guilabel>Video "
#~ "settings</guilabel> and there you can adjust settings like brightness, "
#~ "contrast, &etc;"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui tunned end videoasjanduses hästi kodus, vali kaart "
#~ "<guilabel>Videoseadistused</guilabel>, kus saab kohandada selliseid asju, "
#~ "nagu heledus, kontrast &etc;"

#~ msgid "The End"
#~ msgstr "Lõpp"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Well, we've reached the end of our tutorial. I hope your queries have "
#~ "been adequately answered!"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ja ongi juba käsiraamatu lõpp käes. Me loodame, et suutsime vastata "
#~ "kõigile küsimustele, mis sul võisid tekkida."

#~ msgid "Enjoy using <application>Kamoso</application>!"
#~ msgstr "Naudi <application>Kamoso</application> kasutamist!"
